            <p class="lead">The difference between a host earning $2,000 per month and one earning $3,300 from the same property often comes down to one thing: the right tools. <strong>Dynamic pricing software, automated messaging, noise monitors, and cleaning management apps have transformed how top-performing Airbnb hosts operate.</strong> This guide compares every major category of hosting software so you can build a tech stack that fits your property count, budget, and goals.</p>
