          <h2 id="why-tools-matter">Why Your Tech Stack Matters</h2>
          <p>Running an Airbnb without the right tools is like running a business without a phone system. You can do it, but every task takes longer, errors creep in, and you leave money on the table. The best hosting tools address three core problems.</p>

