          <h2 id="property-management-software">Property Management Software (PMS)</h2>
          <p>A PMS is the central hub of your hosting operation. It syncs calendars across platforms, automates guest messages, manages cleaning schedules, and often includes owner reporting. If you list on more than one platform or manage more than two properties, a PMS pays for itself immediately in time saved and double-booking prevention.</p>

