          <p>Minut is the leading noise monitor for short-term rental hosts. Beyond decibel monitoring, it tracks occupancy via motion sensing and detects cigarette smoke, which is a major concern for no-smoking properties. Alerts arrive via push notification, giving you time to message the guest before a neighbor makes a formal complaint. The device is fully privacy-compliant: it never records audio or video, which makes it legal to use in rental properties across Ontario.</p>

          <p>Minut also integrates with most major PMS platforms, so incident data is logged alongside the booking record. For hosts in regulated cities where noise violations carry demerit points, Minut is close to essential.</p>

