          <p>Guest issues are rare with proper screening, but when they happen the cost in property damage, reviews, and emotional energy is significant. Purpose-built screening tools go beyond Airbnb's basic verification to provide ID checks, background screening, and risk scoring before a guest ever checks in.</p>

